<title>UK: Mardon sets 60 bln yen seven-year FRN.</title>
<headline>Mardon sets 60 bln yen seven-year FRN.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>The following bond was announced by lead manager Sanwa International.</p>
<p> BORROWER   MARDON UNDERWRITING (NO.1)</p>
<p>GUARANTOR  AMERICAN CAPITAL NO 4. INC</p>
<p> AMT    60 BLN YEN    BASE	 3M LIBOR  MATURITY   *12.JUN.04</p>
<p> TYPE    FRN	    MARGIN     -10 BP    PAY DATE  L-12.MAY.97</p>
<p> DENOMS (B) FIVE	ISS PRICE  100.0     FULL FEES   NONE</p>
<p> NOTES	*CALLABLE ON 12.JUN.98 AND ANNUALLY THEREAFTER.</p>
<p> NOTES	UNSUBORDINATED</p>
